      • ACTION_SHOW_MESSAGE

        public static final java.lang.String ACTION_SHOW_MESSAGE
        Activity Action: Show Message
        "com.pax.us.pay.action.SHOW_MESSAGE"

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_PACKAGE - is the package name of caller.
        Type: String

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_TRANS_MODE - is transaction mode.
        Type: String
        See TransMode for details

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_TITLE -

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_TAX_LINE -
        Type: String

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_TOTAL_LINE -
        Type: String

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_IMAGE_URL -
        Type: String

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_IMAGE_DESC -
        Type: String

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_MESSAGE_LIST -
        Type: String
        It is a json list. Example code for read it: 

             InputStream inputStream = new ByteArrayInputStream(bundle.getString(EntryExtraData.PARAM_MESSAGE_LIST).getBytes());
         showMsgList = (List<MsgInfoWrapper>) JsonUtils.readListFromJSON(inputStream, MsgInfoWrapper.class);
     //MsgInfoWrapper definition
     @RestrictTo(RestrictTo.Scope.LIBRARY_GROUP)
     public class MsgInfoWrapper {
     @JsonProperty(value = "index")
     private String index;
     @JsonProperty(value = "MsgInfo")
     private MsgInfo msgInfo;

     public MsgInfoWrapper() {
     }

     public MsgInfoWrapper(String index, MsgInfo msgInfo) {
         this.index = index;
         this.msgInfo = msgInfo;
     }

     public String getIndex() {
         return index;
     }

     public void setIndex(String index) {
         this.index = index;
     }

     public MsgInfo getMsgInfo() {
         return msgInfo;
     }

     public void setMsgInfo(MsgInfo msgInfo) {
         this.msgInfo = msgInfo;
     }
     }

        Input: EntryExtraData.PARAM_CONTINUE_SCREEN -
        Type: String
        Value is always "1"
